msgid "NMRA Standards and Recommended Practices"
msgstr "NMRA 標準と推奨慣例"

#: ../../content/index.rst:6
msgid "This book is a reformatted one of the \"Standards and Recommended Practices\" of National Railway Model Association (NMRA)."
msgstr "本書は全米鉄道模型協会（National Railway Model Association; NMRA）の「標準と推奨慣例を翻訳したものです。"

#: ../../content/index.rst:8
